headline: Buy Stock in These Healthcare Leaders as Q1 Earnings Approach? ABBV, HCA
summary: The medical sector can provide a defensive hedge against economic uncertainty, and investors may be eyeing AbbVie (ABBV) and HCA Healthcare (HCA) stock ahead of their Q1 reports on Friday, April 25.
